body.p: The following Scandinavians bought or sold real estate in Chicago recently:

Ira J. Cobe to Nels A. Johnson: Ridgeway Avenue and Grace Street. Price, $1,800.
Ira Joseph Corbett to Nels H. Hansen: Ridgeway and Wilson Avenues. Price, $760.
